 <item> <title>U.S. Department of Education Announces Grants Totaling More Than $1.2 Million to Charter Schools</title>
 <link>https://www.ed.gov/news/press-releases/us-department-education-announces-grants-totaling-more-12-million-charter-schools</link>
 <description>The U.S. Department of Education has awarded seven Charter School Exemplary Collaboration grants totaling more than $1.2 million to support collaboration between public charter schools, traditional public schools and school districts. Funds will be used to deepen the collaborations and share lessons learned with the education field.</description>
 <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ed.gov/news/press-releases/us-department-education-announces-grants-totaling-more-12-million-charter-schools</guid>
